{"tid":1461872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長輩圖實測！!","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:37:24.000Z","uid":275341,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"33e54ef9826c00766c8c35b346fad3dae73edd49","tid":1461872,"uid":275341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:29:36.000Z","msg":"小妹今日同朋友仔去左貼長輩圖 (A4 size,彩)<br />\n實測威力有幾大<br />\n<br />\n先試温和啲，主打唔係太明顯帶風向嘅<br />\n專去老人區貼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBqw8oG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBqw8oG.jpg&h=a8b170f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n交流比較多係ssp<br />\n雖然本身北河街連儂比較冷清，少啲文宣<br />\n我諗幾張幾張咁痴好吸睛<br />\n所以好多街坊企係度睇，一隻一隻字咁讀出嚟<br />\n一路貼一路有叔伯走嚟吹水，佢地簡直係身同感受<br />\n&quot;生果金我就係攞緊呢個數!！&quot;<br />\n&quot;明日大嶼我有追開！&quot;<br />\n&quot;以前從來冇超支&quot;<br />\n最後梗係提佢地10月投票要識做<br />\n邊個將你地啲錢用哂係其他地方 唔係用嚟幫市民?!<br />\n<br />\n好了 evaluation時間<br />\n唔好怕羞，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>字一定要大大隻</strong></span></span><br />\n我見好多巴絲打畀心機做左好多長輩圖<br />\n但太多字啦<br />\n例如我呢張佢地已經要伸長條頸嚟睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAP2vE0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAP2vE0.jpg&h=ade0f04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(sorry呀ching，借嚟做下例子，希望你唔好介意)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0xLtsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0xLtsX.jpg&h=a318864b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n字真係太細隻 佢地睇唔到架<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">字要精簡，做標題黨，唔好怕留白</span></span></strong><br />\n(sorry呀ching，借嚟做下例子，希望你唔好介意)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7xb8t3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7xb8t3.jpg&h=b5d0c853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁多字佢地都係睇唔到架<br />\n就算係airdrop佢地用手機睇都一樣會睇得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n附送 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">選用顏色</span></strong></span><br />\n唔詳講，有ching出過文<br />\n今日實測後感: 要同底色係contradict嘅，例如藍底就紅橙字之類，所以你地都見到我佛祖同啡底嗰啲唔係咁reader friendly，會下次改進"},{"pid":"9551a2815e9507e0dbebae614a935ed738f45c8b","tid":1461872,"uid":246242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6e24e6109a5ff4c6b7f87f629c7d5878fdc5de7e","tid":1461872,"uid":22197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fe53774da29d86b587e07de854afbd1dddb257f2","tid":1461872,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30c76f1e8c3a91a4869776346d35d60d49380be","tid":1461872,"uid":218412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eac36f7bfe85545c36becd03d82fb594cb0d4ab","tid":1461872,"uid":21002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"字可以細小小 局佢羅老花眼鏡睇 但唔好太細<br />\n要制造人流圍觀 八掛心態"},{"pid":"312c217c3f9a95134e22ffb81d2588f78f5db13c","tid":1461872,"uid":275341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"漏左講<br />\n佢地有睇開新聞，知好多架<br />\n所以大家spin得嚟都係建議唔好老作"},{"pid":"dace524a6f19c9040fa998c013e982c3713acfff","tid":1461872,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"支持長輩圖，唔好畀佢停。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9966af6fae7c0af4ad4f813b8ef7870ba28be0","tid":1461872,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7df1b65705a82818d408080e10e8f174377a39","tid":1461872,"uid":301633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"支持大字彩圖"},{"pid":"e4622a84d0075b045a4ae849e5838c7